values:
i'm really not sure what to say about this.  except that maybe at our next bbq i will serve "frankfurter spectacular"


http://www.candyboots.com/wwcards.html

ok, so i am on day 2 of this diet.  which sucks, by the way.  tonight my kids ate kraft mac n' cheese for dinner.   remember that old commercial for it with the kids singing about the blue box blues?  well, thats how i felt because i love love love it.  once when i was pregnant i was eating mexican food with a good friend and even though we were full, we kept stuffing our faces.  so you know what she did?  she spit on it.  what a friend.

tonight we ate chinese food for dinner.  this was my fortune:  you will soon reach a personal goal.  that is great news because i am starting a diet tomorrow.  its this wonky thing my mom told me about where you are supposed to lose 40 lbs. in a month.  although, im not sure how i am going to track said weight loss since someone in my house got mad at the scale and punched it.  maybe if i feel like it's working i will be motivated to go back ww. 

ps - im keeping this jivejournal

well, this was short lived.  my hubby says he "pays for our family website all year for this very thing, so".....blah blah blah.  he moved my blog.  you can now find it here : http://www.cabreraplace.com/iheartweasley
this is day one. this is also my 29th birthday.  i have never been a journaly type of person, so we will have to see how this goes.  i am going to try and write something everyday.
